The key players in the medical Raman probe market include Renishaw plc, Thermo Fisher Scientific, Cobalt Light Systems, and Horiba, Ltd.

8. What are the different types of medical Raman probes available in the market?
The medical Raman probes are available in handheld, fiber-optic, and stand-off configurations, catering to different medical diagnostic needs.

9. What are the most common applications of medical Raman probes?
The most common applications of medical Raman probes include cancer diagnostics, tissue analysis, pharmaceutical research, and forensic analysis.

